text: Due to the overwhelming public response to our testing events targeting geographic areas and populations disproportionately affected by COVID-19, Salt Lake County Health Department must cancel the rest of the scheduled events, including this afternoon’s, (1/2) #SLCo #COVID19 https://t.co/vJf4b3Vyy9
